>\r\n稍後有更詳細報道。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T07:40:23.000Z","msg":"作賊心虛？"},{"pid":"25fe04296e315995bd84e186a392ba97625dda97","tid":678542,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T08:04:43.000Z","msg":"hello moto?"},{"pid":"59455621114630c71c2c7bf6d47f8b183609673e","tid":678542,"uid":151955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T08:12:45.000Z","msg":"屌，你估佢會識咩，講緊技術野呀，唔係office管理呀，點樣揸搥都未知啦！<br />\n你地咁問法，識條撚答，唔發爛點落台"},{"pid":"fc186ee96fc46373738d917f1172cede1cc320e4","tid":678542,"uid":28599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"信你一成都雙目失明啦，東鐵線觀塘線壞左幾多次呀<br />\n依家傳媒爆左單野出黎，仲高高在上咁<br />\n食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5fb831708c9e110b3b0614b307bad1e5eb535e","tid":678542,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T08:20:57.000Z","msg":"留名等睇垃圾會硬過一地兩檢都唔可以準時通車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234d98b8a34dc2020e67d6d5eee274b5863825b5","tid":678542,"uid":36029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"屌完班港豬咪又照用，撚驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46165fb172bb0f1ee65f79ff7a6abc07ceaed21","tid":678542,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T08:27:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19da96d02ce561b28cb76095746aae0c0020db1e","tid":678542,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T08:27:51.000Z","msg":"不要問,只要信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ca94b70b2a2510c16536d927e6699a884dc8e2","tid":678542,"uid":102356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T08:31:14.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872e5d1809279fa72296d35b84bc6f1802ee09b3","tid":678542,"uid":9542,"like":0,"d